#, fuzzy
#| msgid "Linux has been garnering strength for a number of years now, and its growing popularity drives more and more users to make the jump. The first step on that path is to pick a distribution. This is an important decision, because each distribution has its own peculiarities, and future migration costs can be avoided if the right choice is made from the start."
msgid "Linux has been garnering strength for a number of years now, and its still growing popularity drives more and more users to make the jump. The first step on that path is to pick a distribution. This is an important decision, because each distribution has its own peculiarities, and future migration costs can be avoided if the right choice is made from the start."
msgstr "Des de fa ja uns anys, el Linux ha anat adquirint cada cop més força, i la seva creixent popularitat duu a cada cop més usuaris a fer el salt. La primera passa en aquest camí és el triar una distribució. Aquesta és una decisió important perquè cadascuna té les seves peculiaritats i una tria correcta des del principi pot evitar futurs costos de migració."

