msgid "<emphasis role=\"strong\">Chapter 15</emphasis> is for administrators who want to go further and create their own Debian packages. Finally, <emphasis role=\"strong\">Chapter 16</emphasis> describes the possible future of Debian."
msgstr "El <emphasis role=\"strong\">capítol 15</emphasis> és per a administradors que vulguin aprofundir i crear els seus propis paquets Debian."

